Package at.htl.timetableGenerator

Class Teacher

java.lang.Object
at.htl.timetableGenerator.Teacher
public class Teacher extends Object
This class represents a teacher. A teacher is defined by a name, a set of subjects they can teach, and a timetable of occupied lessons.

  • Constructor Details

    • Teacher

      public Teacher (String name, Set<Subject> subjects, Timetable occupiedLessons)
      Constructs a new Teacher with the specified name and subjects.
      Parameters:
      name - the name of the teacher
      subjects - the set of subjects this teacher can teach
      occupiedLessons - a timetable with lessons that the teacher has assigned. Also determines the no of days and hours they can be assigned. Can be overwritten later.
